00:47:03,111 --> 00:47:06,572
I've come across
a number of articles and content

716
00:47:06,573 --> 00:47:08,407
that interpret the relationship

717
00:47:08,408 --> 00:47:11,494
between Ms. Lee Hyo-jin
and Mr. Kim Hyeon-yang

