00:47:11,495 --> 00:47:13,621
as if it were simply a romantic one.

719
00:47:13,622 --> 00:47:16,208
I believe such an interpretation shows

720
00:47:16,708 --> 00:47:20,254
a complete lack of understanding
of criminal psychology.

721
00:47:22,381 --> 00:47:24,465
<i>The death penalty for the Chijon Family,</i>

722
